 To express romantic interest in a girl, or otherwise, by offering a token of courtship, the first steps are to obtain the girl's hand in marriage, which can be achieved by picking up or taking hold of the girl's hand. After obtaining her hand, ask her to marry you by smashing your face into her face. If the girl agrees to marry you, break the glass on the floor with your face. After a brief period of hand holding, if the girl accepts the offer of
